  "strengths": [
    "Premier defensive support for teams focusing on Melt and Frozen as she gives Pyro and Hydro RES Shred, Cryo application, and shields.",
    "Off-field Cryo application have frequent procs and follows your active character, which makes it reliable for melee characters like Arlecchino.",
    "Maximum duration of her Shield from her Elemental Skill can be refreshed before its duration is over.",
    "Elemental Burst has huge DMG scalings and can be used as a nuke with Melt especially with her Elemental Mastery scaling.",
    "Exploration utility is best for exploring the Masters of the Night-Wind areas similar to Ororon."
  ],
  "weaknesses": [
    "Cannot shred the RES of any other element other than Pyro and Hydro, which limits her universality and possible team comp options.",
    "Off-field Cryo application can only start to take effect if Citlali has more than 50 Nightsoul Points, which means just using her Elemental Skill won't be enough to activate her application yet. This makes her reliant on using her Elemental Burst every rotation, and from satisfying the conditions of her passive.",
    "Shield is relatively weaker scaling-wise versus other shield options like Zhongli or Layla."
  ],
