  "strengths": [
    "Is able to increase the team's damage and his own by merely being part of the team, with the Hexerei buffs skyrocketing these supportive and damage-enhancing benefits.",
    "Can cycle between providing support and being the source of frontloaded damage, with his damage being focused on his Elemental Burst, streamlining his build towards the uptime of this attack.",
    "Fulfills one character out of the two needed to activate Hexerei buffs, and can slot into a variety of teams due to the flexibility of his DMG bonus passive."
  ],
  "weaknesses": [
    "A good chunk of Durin's DMG and RES shred is locked behind Hexerei teams, keeping him from reaching his full potential if placed anywhere else. He is still usable but is highly incentivized to be run within these team comps.",
    "Durin's kit is mostly frontloaded, delegating most of his damage to only his Elemental Burst, making him highly reliant on his Burst procs if he wants to contribute damage in a fight."
  ],
