  "strengths": [
    "Extremely high ATK buffs, giving her the potential to rival and surpass most offensive supports in the game, not to mention that her best artifact is the Scroll of the Hero of Cinder City.",
    "Constellations skyrocket support output as well as improving ease of use, with C6 giving her Elemental Burst a near 100% uptime every rotation.",
    "Weapon choice and Artifact farming is extremely forgiving as Iansan only needs ATK and Energy Recharge to be effective.",
    "Passive Talent gives Iansan some healing potential for the team."
  ],
  "weaknesses": [
    "Maximum ATK buff is reliant on having an active character that frequently moves around, or else the buff that Iansan provides is watered down.",
    "Healing tick is slow, tied to Nightsoul Bursts, and its healing potency is low in comparison to conventional healers or Bennett, which means you may still need other sustain in your party for general use."
  ],
