  "strengths": [
    "On-demand Shield that has the potency to rival that of more premium Shielder options.",
    "Shield is capable of absorbing and adapting to any of the Swirlable elements on-field, which makes the shield particularly useful against Elemental opponents.",
    "ATK scaling makes Lan Yan simple to build but does not jeopardize her effectiveness even if she were to run a full Elemental Mastery.",
    "Constellations give Lan Yan's Shield almost 100% uptime in Quickswap teams."
  ],
  "weaknesses": [
    "Shield cooldown is longer than the Shield duration, resulting in 4 seconds of downtime where her Shield is not deployed. This is also further reduced by her Shield starting at the Elemental Skill cast and not the landing, virtually reducing her Skill's duration further.",
    "Sub-par Anemo application especially Off-Field, making her a one-time Swirl unit in most teams that need to benefit from Anemo's swirl capabilities."
  ],
