  "strengths": [
    "Simple but effective playstyle as a DPS, as it mainly revolves around activating and re-activating his Elemental Skill while spamming Normal Attacks.",
    "Versatile playstyle teambuilding as he can fit into most Mono-Element teams so long as the Anemo, Hexerei, and Elemental requirements are met.",
    "Has a great exploration option built into his kit with his leap, allowing him to cross otherwise impossible distances."
  ],
  "weaknesses": [
    "Can't compare to the top-tier DPS of the current meta due to his incredibly low multipliers, along with his many dependencies such as team comps and Hexerei: Secret Rite.",
    "Versatility loses value in harder content, especially when the content is catered for specific teams that he isn't built for.",
    "Most of his damage heavily relies on his signature weapon as other options are considered subpar."
  ],
